    <!-- Help Menu -->
    <string name="helpTitle">Help</string>
    <string name="helpText">How to play the game:
        \nStart bars
        \nSwipe over the screen in order to start two bars. You control the direction and starting point of the bars with that swipe.
        \n
        \nBars
        \nIf one bar is touched by a red ball, it will be destroyed and you lose a life. When the other bar hasn\'t finished yet and wasn\'t destroyed you can start a single bar by swiping over the screen again.
        \n
        \nClear areas
        \nIf you completely surround an area with successfully set bars and/or the borders of the field and there is no ball in it, it will be cleared.
        \n
        \nTime limit
        \nThe time limit is displayed in milliseconds * 10. You get more time the higher the levels are. When the remaining time reaches 0 you lose the game.
        \n
        \nLives
        \nYou lose a life whenever one of your bars is destroyed. If you lose all lives, the game will be over.
        \n
        \nGoal of the Game:
        \nThe goal of every level is to clear 75 % of the field.
        \n
        \nBots
        \nIf you select a higher number than 1 for "Players" you will play with bots. Those bots have the same abilities like you. You will only get the points for the areas cleared by your color in this mode.
        \n
        \nUnlocking levels
        \nTo unlock a level you have to win the previous level. The levels are unlocked separately for bot mode and single player mode.
    </string>

